column2: Hate this manipulative, abuser
column26: remove Amber Heard from The Stand (2020)
column33: CBS: remove Amber Heard from The Stand (2020)
column34: Amber Heard has yet to be convicted of being guilty of abusing Johnny Depp. There is plenty of rock solid evidence to prove she abused him, and she does not deserve an acting career after what she has done. I would like for her to be recast, so we can see an actress in the screen who deserves her spot on-screen. I refuse to let an abuser go on screen, for millions to see, only encouraging her behavior. by letting her in more movies and shows, we're letting her think her career will be okay if she keeps abusing people. but it won't be. stand with me, let's make a change.

column2: As a survivor of a narcissistic abuser myself, I want awareness of this abuse to be raised and Amber needs to be made an example of, the way she tried to further abuse her victim Johnny Depp by using the smear campaign tactic to cover her tracks and make an “example” of him before he might call her out on her abuse. So she demanded he be “canceled” it’s only fair that she receive the punishment for the crime that she saw for when it was “Johnny” who she convinced society was guilty for abuse... now that she has been exposed it’s only fair, she receive the punishment that she saw fit for him.

column34: Amber Heard has yet to be convicted of being guilty of abusing Johnny Depp. There is plenty of rock solid evidence to prove she abused him, and she does not deserve an acting career after what she has done. column2: As an actual abuse victim, AH horrifies me. She is a perpetrator of violence, intimidation, and the ringleader of calculated campaign of lies and perjury. She should receive the treatment she hoped her victim would receive - she should lose her fortune, her career, her reputation, and her credibility.  She’s a disgusting grifter without an ounce of integrity, dignity, or kindness, and I will boycott any project and/or product she has anything to do with, ever. #justiceforjohnny
